column5: That's awesome... I especially like the we won't jerk you around... nice!!
I've seen a few shops with that name around Florida, also saw a boat with the same name.  Its pretty funny
Tried to name our OFC Tournament team that.........didnt work out.
I went into that shop a couple years ago when I was in Puerta Vallarta.....I wanted to get one of their shirts but they didn't have Xtra Grande!!!  LOL!!!   Chrispy!
I think that was also someones name on here a while ago....that didn't work out so well either!  lol
If someone can have a picture of The Hoff for their team...dont see Master Baiters being an issue. LOL
I bought one of those shirts from that shop last year when I was in Mexico, It is now my lucky fishing top.
Man you need to take a pic of yourself wearing it and post it up lol
